As a JIRA administrator from a huge user base, I would like to set a limit time frame that will automatically set an user as inactive in JIRA, after being offline in the application after that configured time frame.

Currently we have to search in the log in history when was the last time the user logged in, and it becomes difficult when we have a huge user base configured in JIRA.

Having an ability to set an user as inactive after certain time without log in would save a lot of time of the JIRA Admin.

