When adding an Attachment to JIRA, it displays a thumbnail that represents the file type, however the name of the file does not appear to the right of the icon, but under it.

Looking at the CSS, it appears that there is a

{code:html}
li div.attachment-thumb {
  float: none !important;
}
{code}

which is over-riding

{code:html}
.attachment-thumb {
  float: left;
}
{code}

See attached screenshot for a visual example.

